nodes.text: A Dulok with arrows painted on his belly was a member of King Gorneesh's tribe of Duloks on the Forest Moon of Endor. He was a typical green-furred member of his species, although he had a pair of arrows painted on his belly. In 3 ABY, Arrows accompanied King Gorneesh, Umwak, X, and O, and Diamond on a hunting expedition. They were defeated by Asha and several other Ewoks.
